Holdings,%20LP\"\u003eB\u0026amp;N\u003c/a\u003e | \u003ca href=\"https://bookshop.org/p/books/propaganda-girls-the-secret-war-of-the-women-in-the-oss-lisa-rogak/21356863?ean=9781250275592\u0026amp;next=t\u0026amp;affiliate=3214\"\u003eBookshop\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv data-id=\"67f989f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch3\u003e\u003ci\u003eNaples 1944\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv data-id=\"87ac933\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv data-id=\"7237b31\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"674\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://www.thehistoryreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9781250235053-674x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.thehistoryreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9781250235053-674x1024.jpg 674w, https://www.thehistoryreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9781250235053-197x300.jpg 197w, https://www.thehistoryreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9781250235053-768x1167.jpg 768w, https://www.thehistoryreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9781250235053-1011x1536.jpg 1011w, https://www.thehistoryreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9781250235053-1347x2048.jpg 1347w, https://www.thehistoryreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9781250235053-scaled.jpg 1684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 674px) 100vw, 674px\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv data-id=\"930198c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eAward-winning author Keith Lowe’s newest critical deep-dive into the history of Naples during WWII. \u003cem\u003eNaples 1944\u003c/em\u0