/2025/02/9780374613808-scaled.jpg 1707w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv data-id=\"60a172d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThe surprising story of Benjamin Franklin’s most famous invention—and a new take on the Founding Father we thought we knew. As the story of the Franklin stove shows, it’s not so easy to engineer our way out of a climate crisis; with this book, Joyce E. Chaplin reveals how that challenge is as old as the United States itself.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/037461380X?tag=macmillan-20\"\u003eAmazon\u003c/a\u003e | \u003ca href=\"https://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/the-franklin-stove-joyce-e-chaplin/1145466663?ean=9780374613808\u0026amp;st=AFF\u0026amp;2sid=Holtzbrinck%20Publishing%20Holdings,%20LP_7992675_NA\u0026amp;sourceId=AFFHoltzbrinck%20Publishing%20Holdings,%20LP\"\u003eB\u0026amp;N\u003c/a\u003e | \u003ca href=\"https://bookshop.org/p/books/the-franklin-stove-an-unintended-american-revolution-joyce-e-chaplin/21424979?ean=9780374613808\u0026amp;next=t\u0026amp;affiliate=3214\"\u003eBookshop\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv data-id=\"61739ad\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch3\u003e\u003ci\u003eThe Man Nobody Killed\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv data-id=\"073e078\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv data-id=\"adcf701\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"674\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://www.thehistoryreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/97812508982